org.bicycleGeometryWorkshop.report

Enum ReportField

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ReportField>
      • org.bicycleGeometryWorkshop.report.ReportField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ReportField>

    public enum ReportField
extends java.lang.Enum<ReportField>
    Frame Report Fields. This serves as the column headers and keys for the report. The values in this enum define the fields for the report.
